      <h1>Sergio Valverde</h1>
      <p class="role">Platform Engineer @ <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/lunik-explorers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lunik</a> · GitHub Community Spain Organizer</p>
      
      <div class="bio">
        <p>I'm passionate about <strong>Developer Experience</strong>, <strong>DevOps</strong>, <strong>Platform Engineering</strong>, and <strong>large-scale automation</strong>. My professional journey includes roles in <strong>R&amp;D</strong>, <strong>Software Development</strong>, <strong>SRE</strong>, and <strong>Platform Engineering</strong>, giving me a broad perspective across the entire software lifecycle.</p>
        <p>I've worked in environments ranging from <strong>agile startups</strong> to <strong>global enterprises</strong>, always focused on improving <strong>developer productivity</strong>, <strong>streamlining operations</strong>, and <strong>removing friction</strong> between teams and systems.</p>
        <p>I thrive in <strong>collaborative environments</strong> and enjoy leading initiatives that enhance both technical and business outcomes. As an <strong>active member of the tech community</strong>, I regularly contribute through <strong>meetups</strong>, <strong>event organization</strong>, <strong>public speaking</strong>, and <strong>community building</strong>.</p>
      </div>

